{
  "texts": [
    "To our knowledge, there are only a handful of systems where both Mg II and a Balmer line have been scrutinized.",
    "In HE 0435-1223, Mg II and Hα are found to be similarly microlensed (Braibant et al. 2014).",
    "For WGD2038-4008, both lines are found to be free of microlensing deformation (Melo et al. 2021).",
    "This contrasts with the results obtained for RXJ 1131-1231 where a very broad and spatially compact emission has been identified only in Mg II (Sluse et al. 2007).",
    "While differences are also observed between these two lines in SBS0909+532, this is at two very different epochs Mediavilla et al. (2005), Guerras et al. (2013a))."
  ]
}